data.description: Welcome to this 1-1/2 story HOME in Wilton. The main floor offers a living room, formal dining and kitchen with a gas range! Off the kitchen is a bedroom, full bathroom and access to the back patio! The upstairs has 2 more bedrooms, a den, plus an office nook! The lower level has a rec room, laundry and a 3/4 bathroom plus access to the attached garage. Updated electrical panel, furnace and newer vinyl window throughout the home. There is a nice oversized single detached garage with alley access. (18'x24') Contact an agent to setup a private showing today.
